{"tid":2321364,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"建制撐國產疫苗願身先士卒　籲勿妖魔化","createTime":"2020-12-11T12:35:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-11T13:07:08.000Z","uid":230530,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"8eafdc8851dfbdd0a433405bb084ac153498cdf2","tid":2321364,"uid":230530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T12:35:20.000Z","msg":"麥美娟：立法會、區議會議員應先接種<br />\n工聯會立法會議員麥美娟表示，其他國家都有採用內地疫苗，她相信政府採購疫苗的標準，認為社會不應對國產疫苗有偏見，「不應將抗疫混合政治」。但她指，有不少市民反映不欲成為首批接種疫苗人士，擔心若接種率不夠七成，將無助解決疫情，呼籲政府應思考如何提高市民接種疫苗的誘因。<br />\n<br />\n陳恒鑌：不信國產疫苗「可以唔打」<br />\n民建聯議員陳恒鑌指，港府能成功採購兩款疫苗是「交到功課」，認為市民可選擇是否接種疫苗，市民若不相信國產疫苗「可以唔打」，強調社會不應「妖魔化」內地疫苗，因政府是根據科學數據決定採購哪種疫苗。他建議，市民在接種疫苗後可以免檢疫14日回內地，增強市民接種疫苗誘因。"},{"pid":"75f89a0ad872fe2a55683192e95bad6d7c0c6387","tid":2321364,"uid":198181,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T12:36:30.000Z","msg":"藍屍唔打死全家<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b627b27ab0a7bef2fc2e46d16e76cc3555600cd8","tid":2321364,"uid":53687,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T12:36:55.000Z","msg":"黃絲打西方貨，藍屍打中國貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28f1796186fe06bb26d6c4ac67343df1544112eb","tid":2321364,"uid":48851,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T12:37:02.000Z","msg":"from tg<br />\n<br />\n就中國製科興 Sinovac 武肺疫苗，現時所知資料如下：<br />\n<br />\n- 疫苗只完成第一及第二階段測試。其在巴西合作進行第三階段（最後階段）測試的藥廠曾表示，預期科興在 12 月 15 日前公佈結果 [6]<br />\n<br />\n- 11 月的時候巴西曾經因為有志願參與測試者死亡而暫停測試，數天後恢復，當地衛生部門表示相信死亡原因與疫苗無關 [2][7]<br />\n<br />\n- 前幾日與科興合作的印尼藥廠曾傳出 97% 有效率，及後科興已澄清該數字並不正確 [1]<br />\n<br />\n- 科興疫苗使用較傳統的減活 (inactivated) 技術，好處是儲存及運送比較容易，壞處是一般而言產生抗體的效率比較低 [3][4]<br />\n<br />\nreference: <br />\n[1] <a href=\"https://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-china-55212787\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-china-55212787&d=gjdgNhcllSDI%2FgTZdT0hmqbKco4j3WCMPlNn4btP894%3D&h=2822a4eb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-china-55212787&h=e3488d0f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-china-55212787</a><br />\n<br />\n[2] <a href=\"https://www.nytimes.com/2020/11/10/world/asia/brazil-china-vaccine-covid19.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2020%2F11%2F10%2Fworld%2Fasia%2Fbrazil-china-vaccine-covid19.html&d=gjdgNhcllSDI%2FgTZdT0hmqbKco4j3WCMPlNn4btP894%3D&h=dbc4800d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.nytimes.com/2020/11/10/world/asia/brazil-china-vaccine-covid19.html</a><br />\n<br />\n[3] <a href=\"https://www.researchgate.net/figure/Advantages-and-Disadvantages-of-Live-and-Inactivated-Vaccines_tbl1_247870018\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.researchgate.net%2Ffigure%2FAdvantages-and-Disadvantages-of-Live-and-Inactivated-Vaccines_tbl1_247870018&d=gjdgNhcllSDI%2FgTZdT0hmqbKco4j3WCMPlNn4btP894%3D&h=0519788f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.researchgate.net/figure/Advantages-and-Disadvantages-of-Live-and-Inactivated-Vaccines_tbl1_247870018</a><br />\n<br />\n[4] <a href=\"https://www.researchgate.net/figure/Advantages-and-Disadvantages-of-Live-and-Inactivated-Vaccines_tbl1_247870018\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.researchgate.net%2Ffigure%2FAdvantages-and-Disadvantages-of-Live-and-Inactivated-Vaccines_tbl1_247870018&d=gjdgNhcllSDI%2FgTZdT0hmqbKco4j3WCMPlNn4btP894%3D&h=0519788f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.researchgate.net/figure/Advantages-and-Disadvantages-of-Live-and-Inactivated-Vaccines_tbl1_247870018</a><br />\n<br />\n[5] <a href=\"https://www.nytimes.com/2020/11/17/world/in-china-people-scramble-for-shots-of-unproven-vaccines.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2020%2F11%2F17%2Fworld%2Fin-china-people-scramble-for-shots-of-unproven-vaccines.html&d=gjdgNhcllSDI%2FgTZdT0hmqbKco4j3WCMPlNn4btP894%3D&h=ae1750e2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.nytimes.com/2020/11/17/world/in-china-people-scramble-for-shots-of-unproven-vaccines.html</a><br />\n<br />\n[6] <a href=\"https://www.nytimes.com/interactive/2020/science/coronavirus-vaccine-tracker.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2Finteractive%2F2020%2Fscience%2Fcoronavirus-vaccine-tracker.html&d=gjdgNhcllSDI%2FgTZdT0hmqbKco4j3WCMPlNn4btP894%3D&h=9b6b24bd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.nytimes.com/interactive/2020/science/coronavirus-vaccine-tracker.html</a><br />\n<br />\n[7] <a href=\"https://www.nytimes.com/2020/11/11/world/brazil-resumes-chinese-vaccine-trial-after-a-brief-suspension-following-the-death-of-a-volunteer.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2020%2F11%2F11%2Fworld%2Fbrazil-resumes-chinese-vaccine-trial-after-a-brief-suspension-following-the-death-of-a-volunteer.html&d=gjdgNhcllSDI%2FgTZdT0hmqbKco4j3WCMPlNn4btP894%3D&h=1cfcfb8c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.nytimes.com/2020/11/11/world/brazil-resumes-chinese-vaccine-trial-after-a-brief-suspension-following-the-death-of-a-volunteer.html</a>"},{"pid":"232820a5b3fc5b576a9fa269da977d3a3616baff","tid":2321364,"uid":11291,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T12:37:29.000Z","msg":"講得出要做得到<br />\n唔好下巴輕輕<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f7ebaeae2a77b6930d86937321c9a73c18536b3","tid":2321364,"uid":191041,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T12:38:07.000Z","msg":"可以唔打<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n睇死你最後咪又係逼人打<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cfcc27cbcac82aae625df1ad7057b88cc5189ce","tid":2321364,"uid":103156,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T12:39:50.000Z","msg":"早已是妖魔，不必再妖魔化"},{"pid":"fba3e0f777c99adb9378f5c594c31fd9bc14041c","tid":2321364,"uid":158613,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T13:07:08.000Z","msg":"紫驚出嚟撐未？"}]}